column5: Dan, you've posted many photos worthy of placing in contests.
Awesome stuff Dan, can't say much more than the others, well done...  Maureen

You guys are too kind. It was only a for fun contest that takes place monthly on my photography forum. I only posted my result because it was a fishing photo. Thanks again guys.  Anyways, some of you wanted to see the winning photo for the month. So, here it is. Remember, it isn't a fishing site. It's a great photo.
A great photo, but yours was way better!! Probably was the fact that Spiel was in the picture which dropped it down a rung. Well deserved bud.  Your photography is always number one on this site.
j
Dan,way cool,your shot are alway spectacular Great pics of Tep and Spiel
Excellent result for your efforts Dan.  I always look forward to your reports and pics.
Way to go Dan! That looks like it should be on a calander or something!
great as always Dan !!

It was just for fun, but I was thrilled to get second place in a photo contest hosted by a photography web site that I frequent. The theme was "Other Hobbies". So I entered a photo that I took last fall when Spiel and TEP were here. In the photo are TEP, Sis and my friend Joe out for an early morning troll.  It's nice to be recognized by your peers. Here's the original.    And the award that I won.
WTG Dan, congrats, that's really impressive !!  You pictures are always great and I know myself, I always enjoy seeing whatever you offer, especially you animal shots !!  Well done Bud !!

SECOND, what picture could have topped that  Your pictures are always first place as far as I'm concerned.  Whenever I see a thread started by you I look at it to see if there's pictures in it.  Way to go Dan.  Joey
Awesome stuff Dan!  That is a great picture.  Congrats on your second place finish!
way to go Dan, nice shot!  I've finally picked up my camera and have started tackling the learning curve.   Havin lots of fun in the process.
Congrats there Dan, I have always enjoy the brookie one's.
Wish I was there.  Great shot DanC and congrats on your win.
BRAVO! Congrats on the Silver Medal

....Hey now that's pretty cool Dan, well done. You know that most here have told you that you have a great eye for photography and lucky for us here we often get to see it before anyone else. You deserve the accolades no doubt about it.
Nice shot Dan, I love those misty mornings.
Congrats Dan, you always have some great shots.
WTG Dan and a nice shot!!   Rob C
Congrats, I've always enjoyed your outdoors photos!  Mike
Thats great Dan, I remember reading the post with that photo.
Nice picture Dan, congrats!
Congratulations!  That is an amazing shot!  Bly

Hey, thanks everyone. I guess what makes this special for me is the fact that the good people at this particular web site have a passion for photography and their pictures are showing their other hobbies. For me, fishing is my passion and the photography is my hobby. There are some very good photographers that belong to this site. It's kinda like an OFC for photography.
I think you should expand your entering into bigger contests Dan.  I think you would be surprised how good you are compared to some.  You have a very good eye for photography!  Pam
Second place!??Thats a first place pic in my book!great stuff as usual. Joe
Great stuff Dan...CONGRATS!
Congrats Dan! You took a lot of good pics during TP & Spiels visit. The second place pic is awesome but one of my favorites is the forest fire near the lake. Keep up the great work!  Whopper
Congrats Dan that is a good'n, I've enjoyed all your pic's. Keep'em comin...
Nice job Dan!
Great stuff Dan! Now show us how too!
